Add a new helm repository:
helm repo add repository_name

Update helm repositories:
helm repo update

Delete a helm repository:
helm repo remove repository_name

List added repositries:
helm repo ls

Install a helm chart:
helm install <chart_name>

Ugprade a helm chart:
helm upgrade <chart_name>

Rollback a helm chart:
helm rollback <chart_name>

Uninstall a helm chart:
helm uninstall <release_name>

List helm releases in your environment:
helm list [flags]

Get status of a release:
helm status <release>

Search the available chart using the search command:
helm search <chart_name>

Create a helm chart:
helm create <chart_name>

Download helm chart as a tar archive:
helm get <chart_release_name>

Update helm dependencies:
helm dependency update
